<div class="content" name="LINE_DEVSPECIFICFEATURE" uuid="46cb2f30-3271-4d53-9ede-6ac9a881e126"><p>The LINE_DEVSPECIFICFEATURE packet is sent as notification
about device-specific events that occur on a line, address, or call. The
meaning of the event and the interpretation of the fields are device specific.</p><table>
